data.description: A Northeast Albuquerque gem! This charming and newly renovated property features a spacious and airy layout with two living spaces. This well-loved home boasts laminate flooring in all the main living areas, kitchen and bathroom updates, front and backyard landscaping, two outdoor storage sheds, a carport, newer stucco and roofing (2021), and many more upgrades! This beautiful property is conveniently located by schools, parks/trails, restaurants, shopping, and more. But that's not all - this amazing home boasts beautiful and breathtaking views of the Sandia mountains. JUST WAIT UNTIL BALLOON FIESTA VIEWS! Do not let this opportunity pass... this bright, one-of-a-kind home is sure to ''WOW'' you!
